00:08:22.989 --> 00:08:25.509
The brothers then vote Kitty off the boat.

00:08:25.509 --> 00:08:30.539
Before going, she tells Matt that whenever
they were intimate, she was thinking of Simon.

00:08:30.539 --> 00:08:32.190
Matt throws her overboard.

00:08:32.190 --> 00:08:35.630
Kitty tries to get back on board, but Simon
stops her.

00:08:35.630 --> 00:08:37.800
She then slips beneath the waves.

00:08:37.800 --> 00:08:41.349
Simon starts provoking Matt, and they get
into a small scuffle.

00:08:41.349 --> 00:08:46.990
Simon diffuses the fight, and apologizes,
then tries to hit Matt using the hatchet.

00:08:46.990 --> 00:08:51.670
Matt dodges his attempt and is then able to
use the hatchet hitting Simon’s head.

00:08:51.670 --> 00:08:53.940
Simon is then knocked off the boat.

00:08:53.940 --> 00:08:56.750
Matt swims out to Simon attempting to save
him.

00:08:56.750 --> 00:09:00.870
Simon then sees the catfish, and pushes Matt
into the catfish saving himself.

00:09:00.870 --> 00:09:06.720
Kitty, still alive and floating on the overturned
boat, reaches over grabbing Johnny’s necklace.

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:09.620
Not long after the catfish comes and eats
Johnny.

00:09:09.620 --> 00:09:13.790
She realizes that the necklace can protect
her, so she jumps into the water and swims

00:09:13.790 --> 00:09:15.290
back to shore.

00:09:15.290 --> 00:09:17.890
When she arrives, she is greeted by Simon.

00:09:17.890 --> 00:09:23.750
Simon is upset that Kitty has chosen Matt
over him, but then embraces her with a kiss.

00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:28.829
This then leads to him choking her, pushing
her head under water and drowning her.

00:09:28.829 --> 00:09:32.120
After she dies, he tells her that she will
never leave the lake.

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:36.120
A second later, lights shine on him as he
is holding Kitty’s body.

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:39.360
He drops her body and is then confronted by
Mr. Parks.

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:43.100
He asks about Johnny, to which Simon says
there was an accident.

00:09:43.100 --> 00:09:47.970
Mr. Parks then says he was a kind boy, and
that he and his granfather were good friends

00:09:47.970 --> 00:09:49.820
of his for many years.

00:09:49.820 --> 00:09:53.259
Simon then tries to lie about his actions
and the deaths.

00:09:53.259 --> 00:09:58.310
Mr. Parks shows Simon the video camera that
Zeke had, revealing he knows what Simon has

00:09:58.310 --> 00:09:59.310
done.

00:09:59.310 --> 00:10:03.730
Mr. Parks then pulls out a gun telling Simon
to try his luck with the lake.

00:10:03.730 --> 00:10:07.490
Simon begs to be spared, but Mr. Parks opens
fire.

00:10:07.490 --> 00:10:10.889
The first shot misses, but the second hits
his Simon’s leg.

00:10:10.889 --> 00:10:15.019
